      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been so reliable and still runs like a dream! It\u2019s in really nice shape, well-loved, and ready for all your upcoming road trips. You\u2019re going to love how it handles on the road. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
